{"tid":1661046,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"經紀稱現役警買雅居樂樓享八折 大律師質疑或違《防止賄賂條例》","createTime":"2019-10-18T01:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T01:50:44.000Z","uid":68738,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"98698bb2b40094bafc02414fcc76d950feb36cda","tid":1661046,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191017/large/1571319158_42b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191017%2Flarge%2F1571319158_42b9.jpg&h=dbe6cc31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n591房屋交易網站照片／警方宣傳海報照片，設計圖片、《蘋果》製圖。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉昨日（16日）向會員發信，提倡構建鄰近肇慶東站具有「港式生活」特色「肇慶香港城」社區，冀為會員「多一個退休生活選擇」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查「591房屋交易」樓盤網今年7月的廣告，雅居樂翡翠郡一個實用面積880呎、3房2廳單位，售價約為125萬元。《蘋果》致電廣告上負責銷售的維港置業客户經理，他指兩會「團購」的雅居樂項目仍未落成，但強調退休警察購買其他雅居樂樓可申請額外優惠，「100萬嘅樓可以再減兩、三萬」，又稱即使是現任警員也可以購買，而且同樣享有8至95折。<br />\n<br />\n法政思匯成員、大律師何旳匡指出，香港警察隊員佐級協會為會員謀取整體福利不涉利益輸送問題，惟若有現職警員表露身份而獲得相關優惠，則可能違反《警隊通例》及《公務員守則》、《防止賄賂條例》，除非他們當時獲得政府特別許可。<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局表示，不評論個別個案，但公務員如以員工協會或同樂會成員身分，索取或接受商人或公司給予該員工協會或同樂會提供的折扣，如其他組織（例如其他私人公司的員工同樂會）也可按照同等條件享有折扣，而該公務員與有關商人或公司並無公事往來，便無須申請特別許可。根據《接受利益（行政長官許可）公告》，如公務員以私人身分索取或接受商人或公司提供折扣，而該折扣並非只提供予公務員，該公務員與有關商人或公司並無公事往來，公務員可獲一般許可接受有關折扣，否則需向相關部門首長申請特別許可。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191017/60165196?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191017%2F60165196%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizz1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=c6bf7327\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191017%2F60165196%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=fe223fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191017/60165196?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"22d7143a209fd1eb19f5df6dbc927b234c26d0f3","tid":1661046,"uid":50744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:27:26.000Z","msg":"經紀仆街了<br />\n爆黑驚大鑊"},{"pid":"c784a43cfc433fa588986db18c55578ab92c9af5","tid":1661046,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"等佢地簽晒合約先篤灰嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b43f82c2505240f46290b34375af9c7f6d1eda","tid":1661046,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c784a43cfc433fa588986db18c55578ab92c9af5","tid":1661046,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"等佢地簽晒合約先篤灰嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:33:59.000Z","msg":"邊個拉佢地先"},{"pid":"a0e2614a1fe652e4f1f604eef38d5b50088565c7","tid":1661046,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c784a43cfc433fa588986db18c55578ab92c9af5","tid":1661046,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"等佢地簽晒合約先篤灰嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:34:12.000Z","msg":"咪係 都唔撚識玩"},{"pid":"cf23f10d9d96074469c4ae72ee77b7963a7835f7","tid":1661046,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:35:50.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局表示，不評論個別個案 <br />\n呢個政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020a86d0691ba133e938d3451156df4909eab8d2","tid":1661046,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf23f10d9d96